    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1259930/extras/61404f9f50465f1b2d46d517643488d5.avif?t=1745937729\" width=599 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1259930/extras/c144e2587985dc1cd3aae59d59708dd2.avif?t=1745937729\" width=520 height=101 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1259930/extras/f7c9ba0fd3a2e0d686f5c3f759f7042f.webp?t=1745937729\" width=615 height=33 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >流亡者DLC扩充了屡获殊荣的洛夫克拉夫特式文字冒险游戏<i>《密教模拟器》</i>的剧情线，追加了全新的游戏内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1259930/extras/f5815335c077381429a136a270b2f86f.avif?t=1745937729\" width=520 height=67 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1259930/extras/fa90e083cc651e72191a735ecea65821.avif?t=1745937729\" width=520 height=299 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1925年，欧洲。世上存在隐秘的里世界……甚至里世界中还存在更隐秘的地下世界。在可能性的边缘，有这样一群名为清算人的暴徒。他们用昕旦的灰烬账簿来分摊与赊购，将生命，人们想象之中最为珍贵的财富，当成可以交易的商品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你曾是其中的一分子。你正在逃亡。除了身上的衣物以及在赊借来的岁月中获取的一件惊人宝物外，你一无所有。被你背叛的清算人头目正试图榨取你偷来的每一次心跳——即便他们需要横跨三片大陆才能追捕到你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >消失在丝毧麾下无名具名者的迷雾之中……利用你那致命的战利品去赢得声望与财富，开展一段新的人生……或者选择反抗，尝试挑战不可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >流亡者DLC是密教模拟器的最新扩展，颠覆和重塑了游戏已知的一切规则。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1259930/extras/a7bf7bcec2c6e3c0e9b945b78980dc1c.avif?t=1745937729\" width=520 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1259930/extras/f2386c9e4b286bc31c9600ea233586ce.avif?t=1745937729\" width=520 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >流亡者DLC包括如下内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1259930/extras/7ae1695429440c9f6850527c6032f672.webp?t=1745937729\" width=353 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忘掉那些你早已熟悉的飞升之途吧。横跨欧洲甚至朝着更遥远的地方旅行。召唤古老印记。劫掠闹鬼之地。与陌生具名者订下契约。在最短时间内完成逃亡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1259930/extras/f5dbc63676e43efe78a0b4cf779c5a3b.webp?t=1745937729\" width=353 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狡黠；隐忍；痛苦；潜伏；这些还没有囊括全部的可能性。你的旅程何时结束？怎样算成功？怎样算失败？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1259930/extras/0e7e3a2baa81c81fd4115414c44a568b.webp?t=1745937729\" width=353 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那段诡异的匈牙利摄政时的布达佩斯。铁狼治下的考纳斯。在梅沙德与诗人喝茶，在格拉纳达与艺术家喝苦艾酒。琥珀色的罗斯托克，红色的维也纳。亚历山大港，还有隐形的塞拉皮雍。下诺夫哥罗德聚点的最后时光。荣耀的马拉喀什。以及更多其他地方……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1259930/extras/da95feb2c8fa32d575747fe4d4ba18cc.avif?t=1745937729\" width=520 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上一局游戏中如果被波比抵扣而触发了死亡结局，那么下一次游戏中将会出现流亡者的选项。你也可以从主菜单中直接选择以流亡者来开始游戏。</p>",
